{
  "stem": "444.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was-- the first thing in the ghetto, I saw a fellow lying on the sidewalk with an old guy with the hand stretched out and said, give me a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But can you say it for the camera, though?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Give me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an awful thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't believe that you suddenly come from a normal world to a  world that you thought did not exist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you imagine that there was 500,000 population in the Warsaw ghetto, in a very small territory, and crowded with limited food, electricity, and water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could see, and I saw myself, a pushcart with dead bodies they were collecting every morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw it myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I spent-- I was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Again, I-- don't know what to do, I didn't know what to do, where to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I managed to find some soul that let me sleep in-- in a house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew the telephone number of one of the guys' girlfriends in the ghetto, so I called her up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she said they were both in the hospital in the ghetto, but they were OK.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I got in contact with those four fellows.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, I had to have a-- an armband with the Star of David, because I was moving in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's it's a-- it's an awful feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You feel like-- like a marked man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was-- makes a lifetime impression on you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I think the Jews understand that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The ones that went to the holocaust, not the ones  over here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I got the band somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could just borrow from anybody because everybody had that band.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
